---
import modernMockup from "@/assets/images/Modern-screen-mockup.png";
---

<section class="px-4 pt-4">
<div class="relative z-[2] overflow-hidden py-10 md:py-16 lg:py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#BAC7BE] to-[#F4F6F4] rounded-3xl" data-animate="fade-up">
  <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="space-y-6 text-left xl:pt-[70px] xl:pb-[165px]">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-5xl text-text-primary font-semibold leading-tight tracking-[-0.02em]">
            Run Your Construction Business with AI
          </h2>

        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4 text-base md:text-[18px] text-[#414651]">
          <p>From first contact to final payment, your AI Teammate manages sales, residential projects, crews, and invoicing in one place. Handoff replaces the disconnected tools and manual workflows that keep you buried after hours that eat up your nights and weekends.</p>
          <p>Run a tighter business. Protect your margins. Grow profitably.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 pt-2">
          <a
            href="https://app.handoff.ai/sign-up/"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 rounded-xl text-base font-medium border border-border-primary bg-white text-text-primary hover:bg-neutral-50 transition-colors"
          >
            See Handoff in Action
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="w-full flex justify-center lg:justify-end">
        <div class="w-full max-w-[640px] rounded-[28px] overflow-hidden shadow-[0_32px_80px_rgba(10,13,18,0.45)] border border-white/40 bg-black/10">
          <img
            src={modernMockup.src}
            alt="Handoff modern estimate and project view"
            class="w-full h-auto block xl:absolute xl:max-w-[800px] bottom-0 right-0 "
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</section>

